metadata.name: Lunatic Cat
metadata.description:
There are those who live fully in the World Of The Moon and there are those who visit it occasionally. Lucky are the passengers of Existing who at some point know this dimension where it is possible to surf on ideas and enjoy a few seconds of carelessness.

Physical painting created with mixed techniques in gouache, acrylic and markers pens.
Dimensions: A4 8.3 x 11.7 in
